    "result": 12
}
</tool_result>

So Victoria has 12 scoops total. To find how many more scoops Victoria has:<tool_call>
{
    "name": math_eval,
    "arguments": {"expr": "12 - 4"}
}
</tool_call>
<tool_result>
{
    "name": math_eval,
